snippet.title: The Longest Five Minutes — Overview Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS Vita, Steam)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ http://nisamerica.com/games/longest-five-minutes

Our hero faces the origin of all evil, the Demon King himself, but suddenly loses all memories of his adventure. His finishing moves, the name of his hometown, and even the reason he's trying to defeat the Demon King in the first place, all gone. Our hero tries to regain his priceless memories before it's too late, but the Demon King stands before him, his power unyielding!

What can happen in the The Longest Five Minutes!?

Keep up with all of the latest information by following us on Facebook (http://www.facebook.com/NISAmericaInc) and on Twitter (@NISAmerica). For More information: (http://nisamerica.com/) to learn more.
